item-description: The ARAI HELMETS Contour-X Solid Helmet is a great choice for riders looking for a lightweight, comfortable, and stylish helmet. This helmet features a lightweight shell construction with a contoured shape for a snug fit. The interior is lined with a soft, breathable fabric for comfort and the adjustable chin strap ensures a secure fit. The Contour-X also features a removable visor for added protection and style. With its sleek design and superior protection, the ARAI HELMETS Contour-X Solid Helmet is a great choice for any rider. Get yours today and save with Discount Moto Gear * Logo duct works well at low speed and with an upright riding position and can be opened or closed easily with summer or winter gloves, via a short-stroke lever placed at the top if the rider can't see the lever and the logo is in its normal place, the duct is open * Rear spoiler sits a little more forward on the shell and is fed by 3 ports in the shell and efficiently draws air, but also smooths airflow over (and from the side) of the helmet, improving stability and reducing buffeting, especially while overtaking at highway speeds resulting in much less rider fatigue * 3D ARAI logo duct, just 3.5 mm in depth, feeds two central 10 mm intake ports * Logo duct is designed to breakaway in the event of an impact * Aerodynamic rear spoiler with one piece exhaust function * The one-piece aerodynamic rear exhaust/spoiler, operated by a 3-way switch, is inspired by the DF-X2 of the Corsair-X, but redesigned for touring use * Manufactured as thin and light as possible, the aerodynamic rear spoiler is designed to crush or break away upon impact, therefore having no influence on protective performance * Sliding chin vent actuating mechanism is thicker and easy to use with gloves * Designed to fit and connect a communication system easily on the shell exterior and without any compromise to the protection offered by the inner EPS liner

This helmet features 6D's patented Omni-Directional Suspension (ODS) technology, which provides superior impact protection and energy management. The ODS system is designed to move independently of the helmet shell, allowing for a more comfortable fit and better protection. The ATB-2T also features an adjustable visor, a removable and washable liner, and an adjustable chin strap for a secure fit. With its lightweight construction and superior protection, the 6D ATB-2T Ascent Helmet is the perfect choice for any mountain biker. item-description: The AGV Pista GP RR Limited Edition Rossi Winter Test 2020 Helmet is the perfect choice for any MotoGP fan. This helmet is designed to provide superior protection and comfort while you ride. It features a lightweight carbon fiber shell, a multi-density EPS liner, and a Dry-Lex interior lining for maximum breathability. The helmet also has a wide field of vision, a removable nose guard, and a double-D ring closure system for a secure fit. Plus, it comes with a special Rossi Winter Test 2020 graphic to show off your racing spirit. Get yours today and save with Discount Moto Gear * 100% carbon fiber shell * 5-density EPS * Shell and EPS structure designed to minimize rotational accelerations (FIM homologated) * Collarbone safe profile * Detachable PRO Spoiler * Race suit fitment * Metal air vents and extractors (five front vents and two rear extractors) * Visor has 190° horizontal field of view and 85° vertical field of view * Scratch-resistant clear visor with wide field of vision with tear-off pins, ready and suitable for tear-off shields * 5mm thick visor is class 1 optical standard approved for excellent vision * 100% Max Vision Pinlock (120) included * XQRS (Extra Quick Release System) so you can replace the shield in seconds without the use of tools * Metal visor mechanism and patented visor lock system * Cheek pads: Shalimar fabric for soft and stable fit even at high speed * Crown pad: elastic and breathable microfiber * Neck roll: breathable fabric with elastic and waterproof inserts * Sanitized: antibacterial protection * 2Dry: instant sweat absorption * Microsense: premium skin comfort * 360° Adaptive fit * Three-piece adaptable crown pad fit * No stitches in sensitive areas * Embracing neck roll profile * Cheek pads safety release system * All interior parts are easily removable and washable * Removable nose guard * Removable wind protector * Includes Interiors customization kit (top crown pad, rear crown pad and cheek pads), hydration system, tear-off kit
